title: What are some great new song names which have not been written yet? - Quora

response.answer_text: I work in a corporate environment and I would love to write country songs based on the most over used phrases in corporate America. Win-Win - Now that we’re finally apart Touchin Base - A song about infidelities and screwing Throw Him Under the Bus - About a guy (Tom) that tells his best friend’s (Wayne) wife that he (Wayne) is cheating so the guy (Tom) can sleep with the friend’s (Wayne) wife. Do More with Less - Getting older and and poorer every day Paradigm Shift - This one needs more flushing out, but I picture a blue collar guy working hard for an unfair bossman; not getting paid enough. Synergies -Imagine Conway Twitty in his permed hair turning this one into a ballad  So many possibilities….
